videos.description: Penn State's Josh Reaves cuts and elevates, but is met by Nebraka's Isiah Roby who collects a nasty block.
videos.headline: Nebraska's Roby gets emphatic rejection

videos.description: Nebraska's Thomas Allen intercepts a Penn State pass, runs the floor, double-clutches and shoots over a defender for the strong finish.
videos.headline: Nebraska's Allen steals and scores
